metadata.name: The Night Walk
metadata.description:
The day is long gone and night has descended on the city like fog.  
The night doesn't stop, it doesn't get full, it doesn't shut up and it doesn't get tired. Even if the city is tired, it is just beginning.  
It wants to have everything and hide everything.  
But even with a dim light, those who challenge it break through the night.

Photographer: Melih Taner Tanyeli  
Title: The Night Walk  
Edition: Open  
Location: Istanbul-Turkey
